defaultneeded about what the phrase ’95 per cent
default certain
default’ means
default.   Few people may know
default that such an expression in the scientific world is often taken as a gold standard for ‘certainty’ and can be likened to the degree of confidence scientists have in decades’ worth of evidence that cigarettes are deadly.  (Borenstein, September 2013)
